<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ yīn nǐ zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng zǒu guò 迦南771</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yīn nǐ zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng zǒu guò, jiù bù pà qián miàn yǒu duō shǎo kǎn kě.
 wǒ zhī dào zuì xiāng de huā zài bīng xuě zhōng shèng kāi, zuì měi de bǎo qì shì zài màn zhǎng zhōng diāo zuó.
 zuì zuò nán de shí hòu nǐ lái fú chí wǒ, zuì shēn zuì shēn de hēi yè lǐ nǐ bàn wǒ chàng gē.
 nǐ shēng mìng tǔ xīn xiāng, rú yī dài méi yào. wǒ shēn shēn zhēn cáng zài wǒ xiōng huái, shéi yě bù néng duó.
 nǐ qiān zhe wǒ de shǒu, zǒu jiān nán suì yuè. xuě huā fēi lù màn màn, yī jiù zhí zhe.
 zhǐ yào wǒ zhǐ yào wǒ jīn tiān hái huó zhe, jiù yào zǒu bù huí tóu, shì jiè bù néng zài xī yǐn wǒ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>771</hymn_number>
</song>